    "Gamification can be a channel to spark positive change in students and teachers toward IT.",
    "Gamification is defined as \"using game design elements in a non-game context, \" game design elements (e.g., game elements, mechanics, heuristics, and conceptual models), and non-game context (different from entertainment) (Deterding et al., 2011).",
